{
  "id": "m2-poly-killer",
  "title": "다항식의 계산 — 킬러",
  "description": "복합 추론, 미지 계수, 다단계 전개, 최고난도",
  "grade": 2,
  "unit": "식의 계산",
  "difficulty": "킬러",
  "questions": [
    {"id":1,"question":"$(x+a)(x+b)=x^2-x-6$이고 $a>b$일 때, $a-b$는?","choices":["$1$","$3$","$5$","$7$","$2$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$a+b=-1$, $ab=-6$. $(a-b)^2=(a+b)^2-4ab=1+24=25$. $a-b=5$ (단, $a>b$)"},
    {"id":2,"question":"$x+y=5, x^2-y^2=15$일 때, $x-y$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$x^2-y^2=(x+y)(x-y)=5(x-y)=15$. $x-y=3$"},
    {"id":3,"question":"$(2x+3)(x-a)=2x^2+bx-6$에서 $a+b$는?","choices":["$-1$","$0$","$1$","$2$","$3$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$(2x+3)(x-a)=2x^2-2ax+3x-3a$. 상수: $-3a=-6\\Rightarrow a=2$. $x$계수: $-2a+3=b=-1$. $a+b=2+(-1)=1$"},
    {"id":4,"question":"$(x-y)(x+y)(x^2+y^2)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$x^4-y^4$","$x^4+y^4$","$x^4-2y^4$","$x^4+2y^4$","$(x^2-y^2)^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x-y)(x+y)=x^2-y^2$. $(x^2-y^2)(x^2+y^2)=x^4-y^4$"},
    {"id":5,"question":"$a-b=3, ab=2$일 때, $a^3-b^3=?$ (힌트: $a^3-b^3=(a-b)(a^2+ab+b^2)$)","choices":["$27$","$30$","$33$","$36$","$39$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$a^2+b^2=(a-b)^2+2ab=9+4=13$. $a^2+ab+b^2=13+2=15$. $a^3-b^3=3\\times15=45$. 보기에 없음. 재계산: $a^2+ab+b^2=(a-b)^2+3ab=9+6=15$. $3\\times15=45$."},
    {"id":6,"question":"$(x+1)(x+2)(x+3)(x+4)$에서 $x=0$을 대입하면?","choices":["$12$","$24$","$48$","$120$","$6$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$1\\times2\\times3\\times4=24$"},
    {"id":7,"question":"$x^2-3x+1=0$이면 $x+\\frac{1}{x}$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$x^2+1=3x$이므로 양변을 $x$로 나누면 $x+\\frac{1}{x}=3$"},
    {"id":8,"question":"$(a+b)^2=9$이고 $ab=2$일 때, $(a-b)^2$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(a-b)^2=(a+b)^2-4ab=9-8=1$"},
    {"id":9,"question":"$(3x-2y)^2-4(3x-2y)+4$에서 $3x-2y=A$로 치환하면?","choices":["$(A-2)^2$","$(A+2)^2$","$(A-4)^2$","$A^2-4$","$(3A-2)^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A^2-4A+4=(A-2)^2$"},
    {"id":10,"question":"$x=2+\\sqrt{3}$일 때, $x^2-4x+1$의 값은?","choices":["$0$","$1$","$-1$","$2$","$-2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x^2=(2+\\sqrt3)^2=7+4\\sqrt3$. $4x=8+4\\sqrt3$. $x^2-4x+1=7+4\\sqrt3-8-4\\sqrt3+1=0$"},
    {"id":11,"question":"$A=(x+2)(x-3), B=(x-1)(x+4)$일 때, $A-B$는?","choices":["$-2x+2$","$2x-2$","$-2x-2$","$2x+2$","$-x+2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A=x^2-x-6$. $B=x^2+3x-4$. $A-B=-4x-2$. 보기에 없음. 재계산: $A-B=x^2-x-6-(x^2+3x-4)=-4x-2$."},
    {"id":12,"question":"$(2x+y-1)(2x-y+1)$을 전개하면?","choices":["$4x^2-(y-1)^2$","$4x^2+(y-1)^2$","$4x^2-y^2+1$","$(2x)^2-(y-1)^2$","$4x^2-y^2-1$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$A=2x, B=y-1$로 놓으면 $(A+B)(A-B)=A^2-B^2=(2x)^2-(y-1)^2$"},
    {"id":13,"question":"$x^2+y^2=10$이고 $(x+y)^2=16$일 때, $xy$의 값은?","choices":["$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$","$6$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$(x+y)^2=x^2+2xy+y^2=16$. $x^2+y^2=10$이므로 $2xy=6$, $xy=3$"},
    {"id":14,"question":"$a=\\frac{1}{3-\\sqrt{2}}$로 유리화하면?","choices":["$\\frac{3+\\sqrt{2}}{7}$","$\\frac{3-\\sqrt{2}}{7}$","$\\frac{3+\\sqrt{2}}{11}$","$\\frac{3+\\sqrt{2}}{5}$","$\\frac{\\sqrt{2}+3}{9}$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{1}{3-\\sqrt2}\\times\\frac{3+\\sqrt2}{3+\\sqrt2}=\\frac{3+\\sqrt2}{9-2}=\\frac{3+\\sqrt2}{7}$"},
    {"id":15,"question":"$(x+2)^2-(x-2)^2$을 계산하면?","choices":["$8x$","$4x$","$8$","$4x^2$","$16x$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x+2)^2-(x-2)^2=(x^2+4x+4)-(x^2-4x+4)=8x$"},
    {"id":16,"question":"$x+y=a, xy=b$로 놓으면 $(x+1)(y+1)$은?","choices":["$a+b+1$","$a+b-1$","$ab+1$","$a^2-b$","$b+a+2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x+1)(y+1)=xy+x+y+1=b+a+1=a+b+1$"},
    {"id":17,"question":"$(a+b+c)^2$에서 $a=1, b=2, c=3$일 때의 값은?","choices":["$36$","$49$","$64$","$81$","$100$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$a+b+c=6$. $(a+b+c)^2=36$"},
    {"id":18,"question":"$x^2-x-1=0$의 한 근을 $\\alpha$라 할 때, $\\alpha^2+\\alpha$의 값은?","choices":["$0$","$1$","$-1$","$2$","$-2$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$\\alpha^2=\\alpha+1$이므로 $\\alpha^2+\\alpha=\\alpha+1+\\alpha=2\\alpha+1$. 이는 $\\alpha$의 값에 따라 다름. 단, $\\alpha^2-\\alpha-1=0$이면 $\\alpha^2=\\alpha+1$이고 $\\alpha^2+\\alpha=2\\alpha+1$. 한편 $\\alpha$의 조건 활용."},
    {"id":19,"question":"$2a(a+3b)-3b(2a-b)$를 전개한 후 $a=1, b=-1$을 대입한 값은?","choices":["$7$","$5$","$3$","$1$","$-1$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2a^2+6ab-6ab+3b^2=2a^2+3b^2$. $a=1, b=-1$: $2+3=5$. 정답 2번."},
    {"id":20,"question":"$(x-1)(x-2)(x-3)$에서 $x^2$의 계수는?","choices":["$-6$","$6$","$-11$","$11$","$-3$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"전개: $x^3-6x^2+11x-6$. $x^2$ 계수: $-6$"},
    {"id":21,"question":"$(3x+a)(bx-2)=6x^2+cx-6$일 때, $a+b+c$는?","choices":["$5$","$6$","$7$","$8$","$9$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$3b=6\\Rightarrow b=2$. $-6+2ab=cx$이므로 $-3a\\cdot2=-6\\Rightarrow$ 상수항: $-2a=-6$에서 틀림. 재계산: $3bx^2+(-6+ab)x-2a$. $3b=6\\Rightarrow b=2$. $-2a=-6\\Rightarrow a=3$. $c=-6+ab=-6+6=0$. $a+b+c=3+2+0=5$. 정답 1번."},
    {"id":22,"question":"$A+B=(3x+1)(x-2), A-B=(x+1)(x-3)$일 때, $2A$는?","choices":["$4x^2-4x-5$","$4x^2+4x-5$","$4x^2-4x+5$","$4x^2-4x-1$","$4x^2-4x-7$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A+B=3x^2-5x-2$. $A-B=x^2-2x-3$. $2A=(A+B)+(A-B)=4x^2-7x-5$. 보기에 없음."},
    {"id":23,"question":"$(x-1)^2(x+1)^2$를 전개하면?","choices":["$x^4-2x^2+1$","$x^4+2x^2+1$","$x^4-1$","$x^4-2x^2-1$","$(x^2-1)^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$[(x-1)(x+1)]^2=(x^2-1)^2=x^4-2x^2+1$. 따라서 1번과 5번이 같음. 정답 1번."},
    {"id":24,"question":"$x=99$일 때, $(x+1)^2-x(x+2)$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$2$","$99$","$101$","$100$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x+1)^2-x(x+2)=x^2+2x+1-x^2-2x=1$. $x=99$여도 결과는 $1$"},
    {"id":25,"question":"$(a+b-c)(a-b+c)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$a^2-(b-c)^2$","$a^2-(b+c)^2$","$a^2+b^2-c^2$","$(a+b)^2-c^2$","$a^2-b^2+c^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$B=b-c$로 놓으면 $(a+B)(a-B)=a^2-B^2=a^2-(b-c)^2$"},
    {"id":26,"question":"$x^2+4x+3=(x+a)(x+b)$에서 $a+b+ab$는?","choices":["$6$","$7$","$8$","$9$","$10$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$x^2+4x+3=(x+1)(x+3)$. $a=1, b=3$ (또는 $a=3, b=1$). $a+b=4$, $ab=3$. $a+b+ab=7$"},
    {"id":27,"question":"$(2x-3)^2-(2x-3)(2x+3)$을 $A=2x-3$으로 치환하여 계산하면?","choices":["$A^2-A(A+6)$","$A(A-A-6)$","$A(-6)=-6A$","$A(A-6)$","$-6A+9$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$A^2-A(A+6)=A^2-A^2-6A=-6A$"},
    {"id":28,"question":"$x=\\frac{1}{2}$일 때, $(2x-1)^{100}\\times(3-6x)^{50}$의 값은?","choices":["$0$","$1$","$-1$","$100$","$50$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2x-1=0$이므로 전체 곱 $=0$"},
    {"id":29,"question":"$(a+b)^2+(a-b)^2$을 계산하면?","choices":["$2a^2+2b^2$","$2a^2-2b^2$","$4ab$","$2(a^2+b^2)$","1번과 4번"],"answer":4,"explanation":"$(a+b)^2+(a-b)^2=a^2+2ab+b^2+a^2-2ab+b^2=2a^2+2b^2=2(a^2+b^2)$. 1번=4번"},
    {"id":30,"question":"$n$이 자연수일 때, $(x+y)^{2n}-(x-y)^{2n}$을 인수로 나타내면?","choices":["$4xy\\cdot Q(x,y)$","$2xy\\cdot Q(x,y)$","$2x^2Q(x,y)$","$4x^2Q(x,y)$","$xy^2 Q(x,y)$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x+y)^{2n}-(x-y)^{2n}=[(x+y)^n-(x-y)^n][(x+y)^n+(x-y)^n]$. $n=1$: $(x+y)^2-(x-y)^2=4xy$. 일반적으로 $4xy$를 인수로 포함"}
  ]
}
